This JSON structure formalizes the JSON:API v1.1 Top Level requirements as **LegalRule**s suitable for **LegalLean** encoding. All **obligatory** rules (R1-R5, R7-R10) and the single **prohibited** rule (R6) are machine-checkable. The two **defeat_relations** capture statutory exceptions with **lex specialis** priority. **Open texture** in "API" definition represents the key **FormalisationBoundary** requiring implementer judgment.[1]
